{"word":"G5455 - φωνέω - phōnéō - fo-neh'-o - Call","slug":"G5455","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phōnéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>fo-neh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Call"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03C9;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - pho&#x0304;neo&#x0304;</b> - <i>fo-neh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5456\">G5456</a>; to emit a <i>sound</i> (animal, human or instrumental); by implication to <i>address</i> in words or by name, also in imitation: - call (for), crow, cry."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2019\">G2019</a>, <a href=\"#/G4856\">G4856</a>, <a href=\"#/G4857\">G4857</a>, <a href=\"#/G4858\">G4858</a>, <a href=\"#/G4859\">G4859</a>, <a href=\"#/G5456\">G5456</a>"}]}